# IB clientId Registry

IB Gateway rejects duplicate clientIds with `Error 326`. Each script must use **only** its assigned ID. Never reuse an ID from another script.

## Production IDs (scheduler-managed scripts)

These are the scripts actually called by `scheduler.py`. They run sequentially within each job,
so they do not conflict with each other — but they CAN conflict with the dashboard refresh job
(runs every 5 min) and the always-on risk monitor.

